snippet.title: Atari Collection 1 - Evercade Cartridge Tour
snippet.description:
Captured directly from the OG Evercade handheld.
This cart contains 20 games and the systems they are from are listed in the brackets.

Games in the cart:
00:00:15 - Adventure (2600)
00:02:50 - Alien Brigade (7800)
00:09:25 - Aquaventure (2600)*/**
00:12:15 - Asteroids (2600)
00:14:19 - Canyon Bomber (2600)
00:15:26 - Centipede (2600)
00:18:52 - Crystal Castles (2600)
00:20:46 - Desert Falcon (2600)
00:21:55 - Double Dunk (2600)
00:27:24 - Food Fight (7800)
00:29:36 - Gravitar (2600)
00:32:38 - Missile Command (2600)
00:38:55 - Motor Psycho (7800)
00:42:06 - Night Driver (2600)
00:44:22 - Ninja Golf (7800)
00:51:37 - Steeplechase (2600)
00:53:48 - Sword Quest: EarthWorld (2600)
00:58:03 - Tempest (2600)*/**
01:00:22 - Video Pinball (2600)
01:03:42 - Yars' Return (2600)*

*First officially released in 2005 as part of the Atari Flashback 2 console.
**Unreleased prototype
